= SDL_Swap16 =

Use this function to swap the byte order of a 16-bit value.

== Header File ==

Defined in [SDL_endian.h](https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL/blob/SDL2/include/SDL_endian.h), but apps should _only_ `#include "SDL.h"`!

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_FORCE_INLINE Uint16 SDL_Swap16(Uint16 x);</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''x'''
|the value to be swapped
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns the swapped value.

